deck_description:
so, do any of you remember Fushioh Richie?

i tried my best to make a deck that can summon him as fast as humanly possible with the pendulum magician archetype, with a little bit of the zombie engine in their as to give some purpose to his flip effect.

this deck isn't very good, but if you try your hardest, and have the heart of the cards on your side, im sure you can get a pitty win against a war rock player.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

(please ignore the crazy box)

This deck is very cool :)

You can Switch the Trap Holes and <a data-name="Rafflesia">Rafflesia</a> for better traps/spells and other extra deck monster.

I've tested <a data-name="Super Polymerization">Super Polymerization</a> in this deck, but because it takes 2-3 spaces in the extra deck i'm using <a data-name="Forbidden Droplet">Forbidden Droplet</a> instead.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

GLHF
